About Event

​Get ready to thread needles and toast marshmallows! Join us for a beginner-friendly sewing session where you'll actually learn something useful while snacking on s'mores (yes, really). Whether you've never touched a sewing machine or just want to finally figure out how to fix that pile of clothes sitting in your closet, this is your chance to pick up a genuinely handy skill in the most laid-back way possible.
